Author: iron_blanket
Text: Are you seeing the doctor for Ed?   Negative emotions are so much easier to give in to, just sucks they have such shitty consequences.  I'm addicted to scales as well. I went for so long without one. Now I'm back to obsessively weighing myself every time I move. Exhausting
